  caseId: Case_005
  title: Stairwell Footprints
  briefText: "A witness claims they chased a suspect down an outdoor staircase during
    heavy rain. The forensics team found crisp, undisturbed dust prints \u2014 but
    it rained for 3 hours that evening."
