  contradictoryClaimId: CL001
  explanationText: "Petra claims the chase happened at 7:30 PM in pouring rain. The
    staircase is uncovered \u2014 any prints made at 7:30 PM would have been washed
    away by the rain that lasted until 9:15 PM. The dry, crisp dust prints prove
    the footsteps happened AFTER the rain stopped, not during it."
  primaryEvidenceIdA: E001
  primaryEvidenceIdB: E002
